          <title>Russia expels two German journalists in tit-for-tat retaliation, ministry says</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Russia’s Foreign Ministry says it has revoked accreditation of two employees of the German ARD broadcaster and ordered them to leave the country, in what it described as a retaliation to German authorities’ move targeting two journalists from Russia’s state TV.]]></description>
